data.description: Updated 2 bedroom, 2 bath cottage on a large corner lot, complete with a white picket fence in the front yard. Perfect for a small family, roommate, or Airbnb. Ideal location in the upscale historical Summerville community. Centrally Located near fine restaurants and walking parks. Just a few minutes from downtown Augusta, 1.4 miles from Augusta University, and 10 minutes from the Masters Golf Course. The home features a large master bedroom and ensuite with a walk-in closet, and a large secondary bedroom, also with a walk-in closet and a well-appointed separate full bathroom. A huge formal living room, separate dining room and a family room for entertaining, complete with a wet bar. The large eat-in kitchen has stainless steel appliances and plenty of storage space. Throughout the house you will find hardwood floors and ceramic tile and beautiful built-in bookshelves. The back yard is fully fenced with a large fire pit, and a detached garage with a storage room and workshop.
